      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777438534,
      "updated": 1777438534
    },
    {
      "id": "69f18a9800000000001fc803",
      "text": "\tパターン3",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777437335,
      "updated": 1777438534
    },
    {
      "id": "69f18b6900000000001fc80c",
      "text": "\t\t`[友情]`",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777437545,
      "updated": 1777437662
    },
    {
      "id": "69f18b9800000000001fc813",
      "text": "\t\t`[努力]`",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777437591,
      "updated": 1777437665
    },
    {
      "id": "69f18b9d00000000001fc814",
      "text": "\t\t`[勝利]`",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777437596,
      "updated": 1777437667
    },
    {
      "id": "69f18ac000000000001fc80b",
      "text": "\t\t",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777437375,
      "updated": 1777437598
    },
    {
      "id": "69f18b6d00000000001fc80f",
      "text": "\t\t",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777437549,
      "updated": 1777437551
    },
    {
      "id": "69f18b6d00000000001fc810",
      "text": "\t\t",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777437549,
      "updated": 1777437552
    },
    {
      "id": "69f18b6e00000000001fc811",
      "text": "\t\t",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777437549,
      "updated": 1777437557
    },
    {
      "id": "69f18b7500000000001fc812",
      "text": " パターン4？　これはどうだろう？",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777437557,
      "updated": 1777438529
    },
    {
      "id": "69f18ba300000000001fc815",
      "text": "  `[おひつじ座]`",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777437602,
      "updated": 1777437944
    },
    {
      "id": "69f18c2a00000000001fc818",
      "text": "  `[おうし座]`",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777437738,
      "updated": 1777437948
    },
    {
      "id": "69f18c3100000000001fc819",
      "text": "  `[ふたご座]`",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777437744,
      "updated": 1777437953
    },
    {
      "id": "69f18c3700000000001fc81a",
      "text": "  `[かに座]`",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777437751,
      "updated": 1777437958
    },
    {
      "id": "69f18c3e00000000001fc81b",
      "text": "  `[しし座]`",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777437757,
      "updated": 1777437962
    },
    {
      "id": "69f18c4500000000001fc81c",
      "text": "  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777437765,
      "updated": 1777437765
    },
    {
      "id": "69f18c2900000000001fc817",
      "text": "  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777437737,
      "updated": 1777437766
    },
    {
      "id": "69f18c4600000000001fc81d",
      "text": " パターン5",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777437766,
      "updated": 1777440588
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1974f00000000001fc888",
      "text": " \t管弦楽団（オーケストラ）に",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777440591,
      "updated": 1777440625
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1977100000000001fc889",
      "text": " \tよって演奏される楽曲",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777440625,
      "updated": 1777440625
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1977500000000001fc88a",
      "text": " \t",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777440629,
      "updated": 1777440629
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1974800000000001fc887",
      "text": "\t\t",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777440584,
      "updated": 1777440633
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1977800000000001fc88b",
      "text": "\t\t",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777440632,
      "updated": 1777440633
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1977800000000001fc88c",
      "text": "\t\t",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777440632,
      "updated": 1777440636
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1977a00000000001fc88e",
      "text": "\t\t",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777440635,
      "updated": 1777440637
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1977800000000001fc88d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777440632,
      "updated": 1777440632
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1978500000000001fc890",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777440645,
      "updated": 1777440645
    },
    {
      "id": "69f18d6900000000001fc81e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777438057,
      "updated": 1777438057
    },
    {
      "id": "69f18d6f00000000001fc81f",
      "text": "どのくらいの労力でこれを満たせるのか？",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777438063,
      "updated": 1777438080
    },
    {
      "id": "69f18db400000000001fc823",
      "text": "\tパターン3にWikipedia をベタ張りしてみる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777438132,
      "updated": 1777438518
    },
    {
      "id": "69f18d8000000000001fc822",
      "text": " \t友情・努力・勝利とは、『週",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777438080,
      "updated": 1777438322
    },
    {
      "id": "69f18dca00000000001fc824",
      "text": " \t刊少年ジャンプ』（集英社）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777438154,
      "updated": 1777438156
    },
    {
      "id": "69f18dcc00000000001fc825",
      "text": " \t掲載漫画に必要な三大原則と",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777438156,
      "updated": 1777438158
    },
    {
      "id": "69f18dce00000000001fc826",
      "text": " \tされる要素を指す、長野規発",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777438158,
      "updated": 1777438159
    },
    {
      "id": "69f18dd000000000001fc827",
      "text": " \t案によるスローガン。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777438159,
      "updated": 1777438159
    },
    {
      "id": "69f18dd500000000001fc828",
      "text": " \t友情（「志を同じくする仲間",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777438164,
      "updated": 1777438187
    },
    {
      "id": "69f18deb00000000001fc82b",
      "text": " \tを何があっても信じ、護りあ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777438187,
      "updated": 1777438189
    },
    {
      "id": "69f18dff00000000001fc82f",
      "text": "\tパターン4にWikipedia をベタ張りしてみる。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777438206,
      "updated": 1777438522
    },
    {
      "id": "69f18e5400000000001fc831",
      "text": " \t12 ecliptical constellations",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777438291,
      "updated": 1777438292
    },
    {
      "id": "69f18e2600000000001fc830",
      "text": " \t黄道十二星座は、黄道が経過",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777438246,
      "updated": 1777438304
    },
    {
      "id": "69f18e6000000000001fc832",
      "text": " \tしている13星座のうち、へび",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777438304,
      "updated": 1777438306
    },
    {
      "id": "69f18e6200000000001fc833",
      "text": " \tつかい座を除いた12の星座の",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777438306,
      "updated": 1777438308
    },
    {
      "id": "69f18e6400000000001fc834",
      "text": " \tこと。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777438308,
      "updated": 1777438308
    },
    {
      "id": "69f18e7c00000000001fc835",
      "text": "  おひつじ座",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777438331,
      "updated": 1777438342
    },
    {
      "id": "69f18e7c00000000001fc836",
      "text": "  おうし座",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777438331,
      "updated": 1777438343
    },
    {
      "id": "69f18e7c00000000001fc837",
      "text": "\t↑下にリストが出てきており改行が働いている",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777438331,
      "updated": 1777438759
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1901200000000001fc84d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777438738,
      "updated": 1777438738
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1910200000000001fc856",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777438979,
      "updated": 1777438979
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1910300000000001fc857",
      "text": "91文字書かれたページ開いて概ね91文字しか無かったらそれはそれでがっかりしそう。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777438979,
      "updated": 1777439401
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1916800000000001fc859",
      "text": "\t試してみよう",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777439079,
      "updated": 1777439091
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1917300000000001fc85a",
      "text": "  [** 日本国とアメリカ合衆国と]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777439091,
      "updated": 1777439240
    },
    {
      "id": "69f191d700000000001fc85b",
      "text": "  [** の間の相互協力及び安全…]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777439191,
      "updated": 1777439296
    },
    {
      "id": "69f191db00000000001fc85d",
      "text": "  日本国とアメリカ合衆国との",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777439194,
      "updated": 1777439223
    },
    {
      "id": "69f191de00000000001fc85f",
      "text": "  間の相互協力及び安全保障条",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777439197,
      "updated": 1777439223
    },
    {
      "id": "69f191e000000000001fc860",
      "text": "  約第六条に基づく施設及び区",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777439200,
      "updated": 1777439223
    },
    {
      "id": "69f191e100000000001fc861",
      "text": "  域並びに日本国における合衆",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777439201,
      "updated": 1777439223
    },
    {
      "id": "69f191e200000000001fc862",
      "text": "  国軍隊の地位に関する協定及",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777439202,
      "updated": 1777439223
    },
    {
      "id": "69f191e200000000001fc863",
      "text": "  び日本国における国際連合の",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777439202,
      "updated": 1777439223
    },
    {
      "id": "69f191e300000000001fc864",
      "text": "  軍隊の地位に関する協定の実",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777439203,
      "updated": 1777439223
    },
    {
      "id": "69f191e400000000001fc865",
      "text": "  施に伴う道路運送法等の特例",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777439204,
      "updated": 1777439223
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1924a00000000001fc86b",
      "text": "開くと次のような表示になる↓",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777439305,
      "updated": 1777439349
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1925e00000000001fc86c",
      "text": "[bg.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777439325,
      "updated": 1777439363
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1925f00000000001fc86d",
      "text": "[** 日本国とアメリカ合衆国との間の相互協力及び安全保障条約第六条に基づく施設及び区域並びに日本国における合衆国軍隊の地位に関する協定及び日本国における国際連合の軍隊の地位に関する協定の実施に伴う道路運送法等の特例に関する法律]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777439326,
      "updated": 1777439336
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1926000000000001fc86e",
      "text": "日本国とアメリカ合衆国との間の相互協力及び安全保障条約第六条に基づく施設及び区域並びに日本国における合衆国軍隊の地位に関する協定及び日本国における国際連合の軍隊の地位に関する協定の実施に伴う道路運送法等の特例に関する法律",
